OL,3,C'No significant operational impact'
OL,4,Cfrom absence of Police Ombudsman: Long
OL,6,FThere is no "significant operational
OL,7,Fimpact" on the Police Ombudsman office
OL,8,Fdespite the absence of two senior
OL,9,Fpersonnel, Justice Minister Naomi Long
OL,10,Fhas said.
OL,12,FPolice Ombudsman Marie Anderson is
OL,13,Fcurrently absent because of illness,
OL,14,Fwhile the role of chief executive is
OL,15,Fvacant, the Stormont Assembly heard on
OL,16,FMonday.
OL,18,FThe office deals with complaints about
OL,19,Fthe conduct of police officers in
OL,20,FNorthern Ireland, including looking at
OL,21,Fcases from the region's troubled past.
