OL,3,C'No significant operational impact'
OL,4,Cfrom absence of Police Ombudsman: Long
OL,6,FLast year it emerged that the West
OL,7,FMidlands Police had been asked to
OL,8,Finvestigate an incident at the home of
OL,9,Fthe ombudsman in September.
OL,11,FMr Beattie asked Ms Long in the
OL,12,FAssembly whether a risk assessment had
OL,13,Fbeen conducted around the ombudsman
OL,14,F"exercising the powers of her office".
OL,16,FThe minister said it would be
OL,17,Finappropriate for her to comment on
OL,18,Fthe specifics of the case.
