OL,3,C'No significant operational impact'
OL,4,Cfrom absence of Police Ombudsman: Long
OL,6,F"First of all, it is a personnel
OL,7,Fmatter and secondly, it relates to an
OL,8,Fongoing police investigation and,
OL,9,Ftherefore, I have nothing further to
OL,10,Fadd to my original comment," she said.
OL,12,FMs Long also told MLAs that a
OL,13,Fcandidate has been identified for the
OL,14,Frole of chief executive, but they have
OL,15,Fnot yet started in the post.
OL,17,FSinn Fein's Gerry Kelly asked whether
OL,18,Flegacy reports will be impacted.
