OL,3,C'No significant operational impact'
OL,4,Cfrom absence of Police Ombudsman: Long
OL,6,FMs Long said there is a legal duty on
OL,7,Fthe Ombudsman's Office to comply with
OL,8,Frequests from the Independent
OL,9,FCommission for Reconciliation and
OL,10,FInformation Recovery (ICRIR).
OL,12,F"In terms of their assessment, they
OL,13,Fhave advised us there will be no
OL,14,Fsignificant operational impact on the
OL,15,Foffice's capacity due to the Police
OL,16,FOmbudsman's absence due to illness. If
OL,17,Fthat changes, I would expect the
OL,18,Fdepartment to be duly informed," she
OL,19,Fsaid.
